title: Sydney Hightower Talks Life and Love after ‘The Bachelor’
description:
Sydney Hightower stops by to talk wedding planning with her fiancé, NFL star Fred Warner, and how her life has changed since she appeared on “The Bachelor.”   

In their conversation, Sydney discusses why she thanks “The Bachelor” for bringing her and her fiancé together, who she was expecting to be her Bachelor when she arrived at the Mansion, and what it’s really like being in relationship with a professional athlete. Plus, she shares some fabulous details about her upcoming San Diego wedding and reveals who from Bachelor Nation will be standing by her side as she says, “I do.”    

Then, Becca and Michelle get to know Sydney a bit more through a fun round of rapid-fire questions. 

Don’t forget to rate and subscribe so you never miss an episode.
